            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "@tdpsk If request have no body content, the client shouldn't set `Content-Type: application/json` in request headers because empty string is not valid JSON. Thus, server should use `request.form` in that case, and use `request.json` only if client set  `Content-Type: application/json`.\n"
